{"tid":1230520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(RTHK) 自稱休班警員不滿警方過分武力參與反修例遊行","createTime":"2019-06-16T08:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:54:46.000Z","uid":103981,"like":864,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"eba29ca66427041e715b1b1a194bb0f39b895aa1","tid":1230520,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"民陣下午再發起遊行，要求政府撤回修訂逃犯條例，自稱休班警察的李先生在維園出發，他不滿警方對示威者使用過分武力。他表示，不願看見下一代被打，作為老一輩，他願意站出來幫助年輕人，亦希望每一位年輕人能安全回家。<br />\n<br />\n有不少遊行人士帶同子女上街表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n從事教育界的陳先生今日帶同兩個女兒上街，他表示，自己的女兒是未來的一代是社會的主人翁，因此想讓他們知道香港仍有自由，讓他們學習，他反對政府將6月12日的衝突定性為「暴動」，他認為學生和平表達，毋須用武力鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463179-20190616.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463179-20190616.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=34fa4773\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463179-20190616.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3dcf215a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463179-20190616.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ed7362c4917f2a0c14017b49ff606614b395f8c0","tid":1230520,"uid":103981,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7489cbde82ae209797dd4a227e53172eabce42","tid":1230520,"uid":168267,"like":333,"dislike":2,"score":331,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"李Sir，你真係好man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a16e4d29e85ffe00d6c0d3bcf2a932b3ec37961","tid":1230520,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0555912a9fa11d035b077928f509c08df5e181fa","tid":1230520,"uid":47311,"like":276,"dislike":1,"score":275,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"李SIR 好快俾人批鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66a2df78e150c052ac9687f1aa78a4f68ca3cd3","tid":1230520,"uid":117276,"like":135,"dislike":3,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"真警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d6603453838c7621e891a6c19b52af62e77e0d","tid":1230520,"uid":148987,"like":327,"dislike":2,"score":325,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢d就係警察<br />\n唔叫警渣"},{"pid":"9e12cf83d1bcfe878ba320cb91126e18a1721afe","tid":1230520,"uid":3571,"like":190,"dislike":3,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95ef1355b6ee55bf7fce858df9a8cf5552c6bec8","tid":1230520,"uid":134323,"like":149,"dislike":1,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"休班警亞種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 